					"type": 23,
					"value": "Crime complainer occasionaly goes to the Flamist Fist Manip to see if they're any update on his case. He's been mugged twice in the last month and is scared anf frustrated. The Manip and the Fist are stretched thin but she's trying to maintain some formality."
